{
  "stem": "6159.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In which way?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What did you mean by change?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of fear?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, we heard that the Germans approaching Hungary-- first of all, now that I think back, Romanians and Czechoslovakians came in a week crowd to Hungary, escaping to Hungary, and they told us the stories that they catching the Jews and taking them to Germany.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was probably a year or two before they came actually to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All this people who came to-- to escape from-- from the Germans, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's not very hard to hear news when you are in a community where there's similarities, you know, all Jewish people coming and they-- they have, some have relatives.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they say to each other and you get to know everything soon.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we harbored them, as much as we could, I mean not personally me, but whoever could, and tried to keep them until the war is over, but they all thought that Hungary's left out and the war will finish before they get to us.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, it wasn't so, unfortunately, because when they came to us, no matter what nationality were you, that they caught up with you.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was in 1943.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Practically the last of them, but still had enough time to take a lot of Hungarian Jews to concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They still existed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe it was 1942.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't think so, you know, '44 or-- '43, I think, they came to Hungary, 19th of March, I remember the date. 19th of March, 1944?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Four.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the war was finished in '50-- '45, so they-- they just barely have time to-- to kill a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
